,0.08216,0.070977,0.0627,0.054112,0.042558]},{"section":9,"text":"Hmm, so first, the key points here are the sudden drop in academic performance starting in second grade.","dimension":13,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.092944,0.1259,0.11704,0.10555,0.092312,0.081933,0.075102,0.073486,0.062302,0.067722,0.05311,0.05259],"unified_progress":[0.11589,0.088338,0.086565,0.092164,0.090655,0.087353,0.085799,0.084788,0.074847,0.077855,0.063389,0.052361]},{"section":10,"text":"The symptoms include inattention (looking around, not following lessons), hyperactivity (being talkative), and impulsivity (maybe not completing work because he's distracted).","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.10426,0.16336,0.12054,0.09136,0.08035,0.083709,0.071171,0.078299,0.060002,0.0554,0.048427,0.043128],"unified_progress":[0.095031,0.1266,0.10655,0.090635,0.085545,0.08807,0.078642,0.086297,0.07144,0.066223,0.058095,0.046879]},{"section":11,"text":"The fact that his IQ is normal and he reads well suggests it's not a learning disability like dyslexia.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.060856,0.10878,0.11356,0.10704,0.098333,0.093066,0.085844,0.08048,0.072329,0.070561,0.0588,0.050352],"unified_progress":[0.067127,0.092283,0.09506,0.099267,0.09764,0.094343,0.090892,0.087012,0.079924,0.078789,0.06557,0.052092]},{"section":12,"text":"Since his early development was normal and he met milestones, that rules out some developmental disorders.","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.04877,0.092166,0.099683,0.10002,0.097808,0.097932,0.09178,0.087924,0.081799,0.078039,0.067568,0.056512],"unified_progress":[0.066762,0.099127,0.095847,0.096521,0.094542,0.092461,0.089276,0.088223,0.081341,0.077411,0.066274,0.052215]},{"section":13,"text":"The age of onset is important here.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.047862,0.089847,0.10391,0.10551,0.099378,0.091484,0.087116,0.08